data.description: Discover the charm of 604 SE 3rd St, Kerens, TX - a picturesque single-story home from 1925. Resting on a 0.27-acre lot, this 1,258 sqft house offers a story in every corner. It features three inviting bedrooms and two baths, where memories await to be made. The heart of the home, a kitchen equipped with modern appliances, echoes tales of family gatherings. Energy-efficient touches like ceiling fans blend with the warmth of decorative lighting, creating a cozy ambiance. Step outside to the covered porch and into a yard where laughter and play have echoed for nearly a century. Located in the Kerens ISD, this home is more than a structure; it's a canvas of life, ready for new stories.
